author: Solid jj
description:
In this original idea, Superheroes from all corners of the world come to Rick's Pawn Shop from the show Pawn Stars (no relation) to sell their items and make some cash. With Batman, Green Lantern and Thor at the shop, there's no telling what hijinks will ensue. But it will be kept within 2-3 minutes because I got other things to do bro!
